            </div>
            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en" resp="#VM">
                <p>If the inscription is to be read anti-clockwise, as if it were arranged in a circular way, 
                    Arena proposes to integrate it as Γοργε[ῖος κόρ]υφος, variation of the Homeric 
                    Γοργείη κεφαλή ('the head of the Gorgon', Il. 5.741; Od. 11.634).</p>
            </div>
